FBIS4-16419 "drsov074_p_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 17 Apr 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Men 25-45 Not Allowed To Leave Without Special Permit Men 25-45 Not Allowed To Leave Without Special Permit LD1704154994 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1230 GMT 17 Apr 94 LD1704154994 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] Men aged from 25 to 45 have been obliged not to leave the republic and to undergo a three-month course of military training. They can travel to places outside Armenia only by special permit. Military training is considered to be a forced measure, caused by the complicated situation on the Armenian-Azerbaijani border.
